title: MINNECT

creator: Minnect LLC
descriptionHtml:
Minnect enables you to connect one on one with experts and celebrities across a range of different categories. Whether you are looking to solve a specific problem, get advice, or get inspired, Minnect puts the knowledge, experience and insights of others right at your fingertips.

You can engage with experts in 3 simple ways
1. Ask a question and get a text response
2. Ask a question and get a video response with additional text
3. Engage directly in a one-on-one video

Pay by the question or minute - connect and get your answers.

Minnect enables you to connect one on one with experts and celebrities across a range of different categories. Whether you are looking to solve a specific problem, get advice, or get inspired, Minnect puts the knowledge, experience and insights of others right at your fingertips.

You can engage with experts in 3 simple ways
1. Ask a question and get a text and audio response
2. Ask a question and get a video response with additional text
3. Engage directly in a one-on-one video

Pay by the question or minute - connect and get your answers.
descriptionShort: Connect with experts to get questions answered: through chat or video call.
